Collections
 OVERVIEW 
GMC yields superior performance while providing a service to consumers and maintaining its clients’ standing in their respective communities.  The GMC team of management staff and collectors are an extension of your business; we take your goals and produce unique, competitive solutions.  
GMC’s central collection tenets include:

Performance
Compliance
Technology 

Performance
    The team at GMC never forgets the importance of your business.  We forge sustainable relationships based upon superior performance.  The nature of contingency collections ensures that both client and service provider are playing on the same team; we don’t get paid unless we collect on your behalf!
Compliance
    GMC maintains a high standard of ethics and integrity, protecting consumers, its reputation and the standing of its clients.  GMC abides by:
•    FDCPA, CFPB, and state regulations 
  •    Robbins-Rosenthal Act 
  •    Gramm-Leach-Bliley 
  •    Privacy Acts 
  •    Fair Credit Reporting Act 
Technology
    GMC harnesses the latest technologies to ensure data security. As we’re continuously testing new platforms, we’d be happy to discuss our experience in batch skip tracing, data encryption methods, scoring and more.
GMC will service most types of past-due consumer obligations. To learn more about GMC’s collections services, contact us at info@glassmountaincapital.com.   

